   <body>
      <p>Searching and selecting option enables you to add products using the search and select option.</p>
      <p>To add products using search and select option, please follow the below steps:</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Go to the Qualifications &amp; Benefits page and click Add, as shown in the below image.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432767.jpg"/>
            </fig>Product Catalog page appears.</li>
         <li>Click Search Filters.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432763.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Search Filters page appears.<p>You can search for products by using the Basic and Advanced search filters.</p>
            <p>
               <table>
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <colspec colname="col2"/>
                     <thead>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Search Filters</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Values</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Basic Search Filters</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry>
                              <p>In the Basic Search filter, you can search the products using the product Name, Product Code, and Product ID.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Advanced Search Filters</p>
                           </entry>
                           <entry>
                              <p>In the Advanced Search filter, you can search the products using the Field, Operator, and Value.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/102432695/102432762.jpg"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>Click Search.</li>
         <li>Select the products from the searched list, and then click Add.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432761.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Select the required fields, as shown in the below image, for the added products, and then click Save.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432764.jpg"/>
            </fig>The selected products are added.</li>
      </ol>
      <note type="note">
         <p>For each product, Customer Incentive Manager performs real-time validation for all the mandatory fields and product duplication, and displays a validation message if applicable.</p>
      </note>
